item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - Kylie Minogue My Oh My (Redone Extended Mix) Ft Bebe Rexha & Tove Lo [no more LaLaLas edits]
item.description:
I think a great song is ruined by the overly processed LaLaLa acapella style vocals at the beginning and once you've heard them they ruin the chorus also. Here's my take on it...I've removed all the LaLaLas I possibly could and inserted some instrumental sections to pad it out. Hope some of you enjoy these edits. They are in FLAC quality and will be available for 7 days only.

https://www.transfernow.net/dl/202407287FBQRs9W

v2 is probably the most succinct version but not sure I have a favourite
